{"tid":1732591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們 現時最緊要冷靜 同 準備方案應對被捕","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:48:40.000Z","uid":15812,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9a08399d33b82ccd71cf4a52c096fdae0934a8","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"我知咁講係好仆街 但係現時最需要係法律意見<br />\n點樣可以被捕後都無辦法告得入 <br />\n<br />\n同時 唔好亂黎 保住條命<br />\n一日未死 一日都未end game"},{"pid":"5ecbaa91e6004bdd4fe2b2c936f0205b1c284058","tid":1732591,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"e3819695db8f70278dd75f3170096ab1ab54923b","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42bfe4fe404d6870cb7ac0e52edb43094cdadfe","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0f898168f423c1004430bc4c910cf21f66c9d08c","tid":1732591,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【唔好自己出黎，留守扮受害者最好】</span></span><br />\n雖然知PolyU夠勇，但<span style=\"color: red;\">popo明顯係唔想攻入去</span>，因為一攻入去就會輸哂國際線，佢只想你自己出黎，千祈唔好中佢地計，已經好多人中左計被捕。<br />\n<br />\n留番係PolyU，有必要可以落Gear [反正唔應該再衝]。你地要扮 Victim，到時真係被人餓死左，國際線好易打。<span style=\"color: red;\">Press都入緊黎，要扮Victim。被捕時一定要Press影住</span>街坊唔好諗住開缺口，請用<span style=\"color: red;\">人道理由</span>要求開路，運送食物+FA，要國際傳媒影住，popo唔俾，就加強我地國際線。<br />\n<br />\n既然<span style=\"color: red;\">命得一條，就要好好善用</span>，人地重狗，我地唔可以跌入圏套行出去，唔好跟佢地劇本。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Lunch各處開花，到時再想辦法。</span><br />\n<br />\n永遠支持PolyU!"},{"pid":"f9400774bb40c36957c1ca8ba79e54cc812f9e53","tid":1732591,"uid":336769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【校園捉到，好難吿暴動罪】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吿暴動罪要入罪既話舉證責任好高，何況是400+人，我地香港人錢多，不停幫你揾律師上訴<br />\n<br />\n係校園入面比人拉只可以懷疑你參與暴動，而好難有確實環境證據<br />\n<br />\n同衝突現場被拉完全唔同"},{"pid":"4fc8f62bdf5fad55435d3dbec229e73296e9d8df","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c076eacf0cf7574b280b90eb0968725ebb7bcc9","tid":1732591,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b46ec627e1cd4b424f8304cd39a406181b8be187","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"你身上乜鳩都無係告你唔到"},{"pid":"bd132fcf3ab6d841c59df6a9b3a19c5396540eda","tid":1732591,"uid":190401,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d9a08399d33b82ccd71cf4a52c096fdae0934a8","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"我知咁講係好仆街 但係現時最需要係法律意見<br />\n點樣可以被捕後都無辦法告得入 <br />\n<br />\n同時 唔好亂黎 保住條命<br />\n一日未死 一日都未end game"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:33:30.000Z","msg":"係呀，投降輸一半。唔係性命都補不住"},{"pid":"efe22769ab1b29219f90bef542e9d0c90b00a634","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd132fcf3ab6d841c59df6a9b3a19c5396540eda","tid":1732591,"uid":190401,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d9a08399d33b82ccd71cf4a52c096fdae0934a8","tid":1732591,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0